# =============================================================================
# Epigenetic clock reproduction — Git ignore rules
# =============================================================================
# Large GEO supplements, full methylation matrices, and all analysis exports
# are regenerated by the notebooks. Keeping them out of Git avoids multi‑GB
# remotes, licensing ambiguity for redistributed assay files, and stale
# results that drift from the committed code. Clone + pip + Run All reproduces
# data/processed/ and results/ locally.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Jupyter
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python bytecode & packaging artifacts
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Virtual environments
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Downloaded & generated data (see .gitkeep for empty directory placeholders)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Raw GEO SOFT tables, gzipped beta matrices, Illumina manifests, etc.
data/raw/*
!data/raw/.gitkeep

# Processed X/y/metadata — reproducible outputs of 01_data_loading.ipynb
data/processed/*
!data/processed/.gitkeep

# Metrics, figures, enrichment tables — reproducible outputs of 02 / 03
results/*
!results/.gitkeep

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS & editor clutter
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional: local secrets or machine-specific config (uncomment if needed)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .env
# *.local
